<img src="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/local--files/scp-style-resource/header5.png" alt="header5.png" class="image" />
<hr />
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size:300%;"><span style="color: red"><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">正在验证许可信息</span></strong></span></span></p>
